highlights.text: Maan Meri Jaan by King has been on Top Songs Mumbai the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
Pritam has the most spots on Top Songs Mumbai. Kesariya is the highest at #3.
Na Ja by Pav Dharia is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Mumbai, up 17 spots at #80.
Character Dheela 2.0 (From "Shehzada") by Pritam, Amitabh Bhattacharya, Neeraj Shridhar, Abhijit Vaghani, and Ashish Pandit is the highest new entry on Top Songs Mumbai at #36.
